import { createStore } from 'redux'
import { combineReducers } from 'redux'
import appReducer from './src/reducers/appReducer'
import searchReducer from './src/reducers/searchReducer'
import authReducer from './src/reducers/authReducer'
import productReducer from './src/reducers/productsReducer'
import invoiceReducer from './src/reducers/invoicesReducer'
import cartsReducer from './src/reducers/cartsReducer'

const reducers = combineReducers({
  appReducer,
  searchReducer,
  authReducer,
  productReducer,
  invoiceReducer,
  cartsReducer
})

export default createStore(reducers)
